Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: grub2-once
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, perl
Description: Set the default boot entry for the next boot only.
 Tool which reads all active bootloader entries from grub and
 preselects active entries for the boot process.
 Reset selection to default on next normal boot.
